createElection(string,string,uint256,uin.details: use this to deploy new Election contracts and reset the temporary options lists afterwards

params._description: specifies the description of the election
params._startTime: specifies the beginning of the election (since Unix Epoch in seconds)
params._timeLimit: specifies a time limit until when the election is open (since Unix Epoch in seconds)
params._title: specifies the name of the election (e.g. national elections)
